Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okinawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're even scheduled to go scuba diving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.56,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\c&H000000&\fs80\pos(717.909,43)}Schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.56,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\c&H000000&\fs70\pos(525.545,196.5)}Day 2
