Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.56,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\an3\c&H000000&\pos(800.864,629.75)}{\fs65}Scuba Diving\N{\fs45}(first time)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.56,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\c&H000000&\an3\pos(799.682,823.5)}{\fs65}Lunch\N{\fs45}(boxed)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.56,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\c&H000000&\an3\pos(802.5,940.25)}{\fs65}Scuba Diving\N{\fs45}(second time)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Scuba diving...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, it's been\Nthree years since I've gone diving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, where did you go for your school trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we didn't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:26.00,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\be1\pos(314.045,853)}{\fs65}EPISODE 10\N{\fs90}MAGMA DIVER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go on the trip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're on standby for combat duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You never told me anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I just told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the hell decided that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, the Operations Planning Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you stop slurping that tea\Nand say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a man, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I kind of anticipated\Nit would be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've already given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How pathetic. Nothing's more useless\Nthan a housebroken male.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't talk about me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you must feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's just no helping this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's always the possibility of\Nan Angel attack while you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always standby!\NStandby, standby, standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We've always got to be ready to defend\Nagainst an enemy who may not even come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try to find out where they are,\Nand attack them for once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could do that,\Nwe'd have already done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, think of this as a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,While the rest of your class is on the trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the two of you can study a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you think I don't know about these?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're greatly mistaken if you thought\NI wouldn't find out about these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What you get on your tests at school\Nis piped directly to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ridiculous. Who cares about grades?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:04:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got absolutely no interest in\Nthe old-fashioned grading system.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When in Rome, do as the Romans do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to adjust to Japanese school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, I'll bring you some souvenirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just too bad for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have enough fun for both of ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Paste the observation data on Mt. Asama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,from Balthasar to Melchior\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A school trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty carefree for times like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because the times are so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that they want to have a little fun\Nwhile they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Studying science.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a diligent student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say that, but I have to do it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta da!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I can't go scuba diving in Okinawa,\NI'm going to do it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. What're you working on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't solve an easy equation like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you solve a difficult\Nproblem like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and not make good grades on your tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I couldn't figure out\Nwhat the questions said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you couldn't read\Nthe questions in Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I haven't learned all\Nthe Chinese characters yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't study it in college over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,College?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I graduated last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what does this one say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about thermal expansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thermal expansion? That's kid stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it simply,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:06:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,things expand when they get hot,\Nand shrink when they get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to warm up just my breasts,\Ndo you think they'd grow a little bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What a boring guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this, Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Back roll entry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This just isn't clear enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But just as the report from Mt. Asama\NEarthquake Research Laboratory says,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,this shadow is definitely suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, we can't ignore this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the Magi's judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifty-fifty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Katsuragi's already on site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. Another 500, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Depth 1200. The pressure resistant\Npartition is cracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Katsuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If it breaks, we'll pay for the damage.\N200 more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're monitoring a reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin analysis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The probe has imploded due\Nto the extreme pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the analysis?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just barely made it. The pattern is blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt, it's an Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As of now, this laboratory will be\Ncompletely sealed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's under Nerv's jurisdiction now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Any and all access to the outside\Nworld is prohibited,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and all records of the events of the\Npast six hours are classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:14.84,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}{\pos(1083.2,221.4)\fs40}Seismic Wave Analysis Room 2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:14.84,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}{\fs75\pos(1082.727,742.5)}Seismic Wave Analysis Room 1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Request an A-17 from Commander lkari,\Ntop priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch what you're saying.\NThis is an open line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Hurry up and switch\Nto a scrambled line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A-17?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to launch an offensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Unacceptable, it's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You had better not say you've forgotten\Nwhat happened fifteen years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a chance to move from\Na consistently defensive posture
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to an offensive one for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The risk is too large.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'm sure you're aware how\Nimportant a live Angel sample would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We will not tolerate failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If we fail, it will result in the extinction\Nof the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's something like a chrysalis\Nprior to reaching the adult stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This operation's prime objective\Nis to capture this Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We must capture it alive, as close\Nto its original state as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you must destroy it immediately.\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The designated pilot for\Nthe actual operation is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let me! I'll dive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll bet it's going to be me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry out the mission using Unit 02.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! This'll be a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The prototype Unit 00 isn't compatible with\Nthe special equipment we'll be using.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei and Unit 00 will remain at\Nheadquarters on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get to go to the hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Since an A-17 has been ordered,\Nwe'll scramble immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You say this is the heat resistant plug suit,\Nbut it's not any different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Try pressing the switch on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 02 is also ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No! What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The suit is designed to protect you from\Nheat, pressure, and radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Type-D equipment, for combat\Nunder extreme environmental duress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that my Unit 02?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Count me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to appear in public in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This sort of thing is up Shinji's alley!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was anticipating seeing Asuka's\Ngallant figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have the courage to go\Nin front of Mr. Kaji looking so uncool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go in Unit 02.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't want you\Ntouching my Unit 02!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather do it than let\Nthe First take my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's uncool, but put up with it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Units 01 and 02 have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Have both units stand by in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Move in the laser bore, and ready the crane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom arm fixed in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Coolant circulation system going on auto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Mr. Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That jerk won't be here.\NThere's nothing for him to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I wanted him to see how great I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, an A-17 has been ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes the freeze of all current assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are many people who\Nwill be put out by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have any excuse.\NThe order was official.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Nerv fails, it'll mean\Nthe end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not that arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The UN's Air Force is on standby alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Until this mission has been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they going to help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're here to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In case we fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They will use N2 depth charges to\Ndestroy the Angel, and us with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would order something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser operation, complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The bore path has been secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Type D equipment\Nis functioning normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 02 is in position to dispatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 02 is entering the lava.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this, Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant stroke entry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Current depth, 170. Speed of descent, 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Visibility is zero. I can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Switching to CT monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with this, visibility is no more than 120.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Depth, 400...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,450...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,500...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,550...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,600...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,650...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,900...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,950...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,1000...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,1020...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're over the maximum safe depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Depth is 1300. Estimated target level.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, can you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No reactions detected. It's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the lava current\Nis faster than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The target's velocity doesn't\Nmatch our predictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and re-calculate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue the operation. Resume descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Depth, 1350...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,1400...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A crack has occurred in\Nthe second coolant pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Depth, 1480...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're over the maximum allowed depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't made contact with the target yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're still good. I just want to\Nhurry up, finish this, and take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a nice hot spring near here.\NWe'll hit it once we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maximum allowed depth plus 120.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Unit 02 has lost its prog knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maximum allowed depth plus 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Katsuragi, any more than this and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a human on board this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am in charge of this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceed, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Misato's right. I'm okay. I can keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Depth, 1780...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We've reached the adjusted target depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Visual confirmation of the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to capture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you are being moved\Nby convection currents,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so you'll only have one chance\Nto make contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,T-minus 30 to contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Relative velocity 2.2. I'm now on the axis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Electromagnetic cage deployed.\NNo problems detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The target has been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:15:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice one, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture operation completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Fear is often worse\Nthan the danger, as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It really was a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is more of a sauna suit\Nthan a plug suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to get to the hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the tension let loose all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You were scared about this operation too,\Nweren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, because if we handled it badly,\Nwe'd have had a repeat performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, the Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need another of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good! It's started to emerge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much earlier than we predicted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Status of the cage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No way it can hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Abort the capture! Jettison the cage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're changing the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroying the Angel is now top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 02, prepare for combat as you withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What I've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I forgot I dropped the knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right in front!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Releasing ballast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad. I've lost sight of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to that, I've got lousy visibility,\NI'm really hot,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and this suit's plastered to me\Nand feels disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This really sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take this chance to drop you\NUnit 01's knife. Catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Have you dropped it yet, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact with knife, 40 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Angel is approaching rapidly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable! How could it open its mouth\Nin such an environment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Its construction must be incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Left leg damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Engage heat shields!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If it can withstand such a high heat,\Nhigh pressure environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,then the prog knife will be useless against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Thermal expansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer all coolant pressure\Nto cable three! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right when I succeeded...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, don't go overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:03.09,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\pos(902.727,363.55)\c&H011A2C&\fs50}Oomiya
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:08.01,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}{\frx354\fry4\fs85\an1\frz0.0009155\pos(772.8,531.8)\c&HA6928E&}Welcome\NNerv\NParty
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone from Nerv here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your signature here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,From Mr. Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The bath is over there, to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew a bath could feel this good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you throw me the body shampoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We ran out of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Watch where you're throwing!\NYou suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hit me in some weird spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, your skin is so soft and smooth, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! You're tickling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How about right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it doesn't wear out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It expanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this? I got this in the Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You know all about my past, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah. It's part of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all ancient history for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't let it bother us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:22:00.59,TBC Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.75}{\pos(1540.4,729.6)}TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:06.99,Preview Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.75}PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.44,0:23:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who don't think well of Nerv cut off\Nthe power supply to all of New Tokyo-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.41,0:23:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With none of the modern facilities\Noperational, an Angel closes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: "In the Still Darkness"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:21.04,ED Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}IN THE STILL DARKNESS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Expect more fan service next time too!
